<div class="hms">
    <div class="box">
        <div class="box-title"><h2>{TERM} On-campus Housing Re-application</h2></div>
        <div class="box-content">
        Welcome to Appalachian State University Housing and Residence Life. As a returning student you must re-apply and be selected in order to be guaranteed on-campus housing for {TERM}. Students will be selected at random. If you are selected you will be notified by email.
        
        <strong>For more information on how the selection process works, please read the <a href="https://hms.appstate.edu/webpage/3" target="_blank">housing re-application FAQ</a>.</strong><br />
        <br />
        {START_FORM}
        <table>
            <tr>
                <th colspan="2">Contact Information</th>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td colspan="2">
                    We'll only use this information to contact you in case we have a question about your application or if you receive a package (via UPS, FedEx, etc). This information will not be shared with anyone else.
                </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Cell Phone Number: </td><td align="left">({AREA_CODE})-{EXCHANGE}-{NUMBER}</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td></td>
                <td>{DO_NOT_CALL}<sub>Check here if you do not have a cell phone or do not wish to provide your cell phone number.</sub></td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <th colspan="2">Preferred Roommates</th>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td colspan="2">
                    Below you may (optionally) provide the <b>ASU user names</b> of up to three of your <strong>preferred</strong> roommates. <strong>These are only your <em>preferred</em> roommates. You will have the opportunity to choose your actual roommates after you are invited to select a room. We cannot guarantee that you will be assigned with your preferred roommates.</strong> However, we will notify the students you list below of your desire to be roommates and invite them to re-apply for on-campus housing (if they have not already).<br /><br />
                </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>First roommate: </td>
                <td>{ROOMMATE1}@appstate.edu</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Second roommate: </td>
                <td>{ROOMMATE2}@appstate.edu</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Third roommate: </td>
                <td>{ROOMMATE3}@appstate.edu</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <th colspan="2">Meal Plan</th>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td colspan="2">Please choose a meal plan. You'll have the opportunity to change this again later (after you choose your room).</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>{MEAL_PLAN_LABEL}</td>
                <td>{MEAL_PLAN}</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <th colspan="2">Special Interest Housing</th>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td colspan="2">To re-apply for housing with a particular program on-campus, select that group in the box below. Each group/program may have a separate (on-line or paper-based) application to complete. If you are approved by the group/program you apply for, then you will be administratively assigned and may not be able to choose your room.</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>{SPECIAL_INTEREST_LABEL}</td>
                <td>{SPECIAL_INTEREST}</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <th colspan="2">Special needs</th>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td colspan="2">{SPECIAL_NEED}&nbsp;{SPECIAL_NEED_LABEL}</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <th colspan="2">Terms & Conditions</th>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td colspan="2">{DEPOSIT_CHECK}{DEPOSIT_CHECK_LABEL}</td>
            </tr>
        </table>
        <br />
        <br />
        {SUBMIT}
        {END_FORM}
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
